            sample = multivariate_normal.rvs(mean=[60, 50],
                                            cov=[[160, 0], [0, 80]],
                                            size=size,
                                            random_state=94)
            round_vec = np.vectorize(round)
            sample = round_vec(sample)
            return [x.tolist() for x in sample]
